NC: Fight Declared No Contest Fighter Bio Career Justin Robert Levens (born April 18, 1980 in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania) is an American professional mixed martial arts (MMA) fighter. He is currently fighting for the Southern California Condors of the International Fight League. Levens grew up fast in the streets of Philadelphia, before eventually moving across the country for a chance at a better life. He found that life in Newport Beach, California, where he learned to channel his aggressive energy into a more productive form.
